Package edu.blooddonor.geoAPI

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DistanceListActivity
    Activity displaying list of Stations with relative distances (wrt. current position).
    DistanceMatrixTask
    Async Task getting distances and travel times between Stations and given location of user (using Google Maps Distance Matrix API).
    GeocodingQuery
    Collection of static methods used to communicate with Google Maps APIs, parsing JSON responses.
    MapsActivity
    Activity displaying map (Google Maps API) with Stations and current position marked.
    UpdateStationGeoTask
    Async Task updating database Stations entries in case of geographical coordinates missing (using queries to Google Maps Geocoding API).
